{"tid":1537220,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同我搞到「我是中國人」都會比大陸禁","createTime":"2019-09-04T00:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T00:54:44.000Z","uid":262017,"like":23,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"0c46712e45a620492ddf67ec94b3451f66fa4f01","tid":1537220,"uid":262017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T00:30:07.000Z","msg":"試下文宜，口號叫<br />\n<br />\n「我是中國人，人民不當家」<br />\n「我愛中國，中國不愛我」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n內容字眼可以再改，中國/祖國。方向係「被禁」，連講愛中國都被禁，試問佢地有咩感想，每次佢地問你係咪中國人，可以直接咁回應佢地<br />\n<br />\n我知難聽過粗口，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">但係佢地起國内最有感受</span>，一但成功，對家無辨法將我地打成港獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而且佢地聽到第一句最入腦，咁先唔會被block左聲音。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">如果起中國連 我是中國人 都會被禁，佢地先會識醒下，雖然可能得幾秒</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n逆向思維，大家自由發揮，求文宣出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ba5035012b3e28f6b20aec8a2639c301fd19b7","tid":1537220,"uid":2419,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T00:31:28.000Z","msg":"你叫埋我果份 唔割"},{"pid":"dc31c8e1af9e109955f7d9e8aa6dfa7e4fd869f2","tid":1537220,"uid":229436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T00:31:30.000Z","msg":"可以"},{"pid":"495f3507e82451985d91bc65ebce6b55e829c09a","tid":1537220,"uid":262017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T00:33:04.000Z","msg":"人地黎搞事，勇武都忍到去同人影合照，大家唔係搞唔掂掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb2854aec9ed71715ebb34b540d903410a341d7","tid":1537220,"uid":262017,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"30ba5035012b3e28f6b20aec8a2639c301fd19b7","tid":1537220,"uid":2419,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T00:31:28.000Z","msg":"你叫埋我果份 唔割"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T00:35:20.000Z","msg":"共產黨不等於中國，中國人我忍到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對面冇左